---
<BlogLayout
  title="Chinese Sentence Structure: The Complete Grammar Guide"
  description="Master Chinese sentence structure from SVO basics to complex patterns. Learn time/place placement, negation (不 vs 没), question formation, essential particles, and 10 core sentence patterns with examples."
  language="chinese"
  category="grammar"
  tags={["grammar", "sentence-structure", "beginner", "particles"]}
  publishDate="2026-02-19"
